      <title>沙特阿美在美国和伦敦举办路演吸引外国投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/aramco-share-sale-saudis-woo-foreign-investors-with-us-london-roadshows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司的高管将在伦敦和美国举办一系列活动，以吸引人们对该石油巨头 120 亿美元股票发售的需求。五年前，沙特阿美取消了首次公开募股的国际路演。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/aramco-share-sale-saudis-woo-foreign-investors-with-us-london-roadshows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:28:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非大选后纷争让投资者陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非大选未能产生绝对胜利者，联盟谈判的结果仍存在很大不确定性，投资者准备迎接南非金融市场的进一步动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查预测莫迪获胜，印度股市创下新高，卢比上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/india-s-stock-futures-rally-as-polls-predict-landslide-modi-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在出口民意调查显示总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党取得压倒性胜利后，印度股市飙升至历史最高水平，而卢比和主权债券价格也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/india-s-stock-futures-rally-as-polls-predict-landslide-modi-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
